{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://leoshcn.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Fanny Cochrane Smith (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that recordings of the voice of <b><a href=\"/wiki/Fanny_Cochrane_Smith\" title=\"Fanny Cochrane Smith\">Fanny Cochrane Smith</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> were used in the development of a modern Aboriginal Tasmanian constructed language?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fanny_Cochrane_Smith","retrieved":1772087582260},{"title":"The Missing (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/The_Missing_(2023_film)\" title=\"The Missing (2023 film)\">The Missing</a></b></i> took three years to write but only four days to film?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Missing_(2023_film)","retrieved":1772087582260},{"title":"Chicago State Cougars football (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Chicago_State_Cougars_football\" title=\"Chicago State Cougars football\">Chicago State Cougars football</a></b> is the only <a href=\"/wiki/NCAA_Division_I\" title=\"NCAA Division I\">NCAA Division&nbsp;I</a> gridiron football program in Chicago?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chicago_State_Cougars_football","retrieved":1772087582260},{"title":"2021 Liechtenstein general election (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that only 42 votes separated the two major parties in the <b><a href=\"/wiki/2021_Liechtenstein_general_election\" title=\"2021 Liechtenstein general election\">2021 Liechtenstein general election</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2021_Liechtenstein_general_election","retrieved":1772087582272},{"title":"Renegade II (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the space-combat simulation game <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Renegade_II:_Return_to_Jacob%27s_Star\" title=\"Renegade II: Return to Jacob's Star\">Renegade&nbsp;II</a></b></i> was cancelled for poor quality despite the release of demo and beta versions and reviews?","li